  <p class="lead">This page summarises the information you <em>can</em> find in a birth, marriage or death Certificate — much more than the basic details shown in the Indexes. Only the GRO Indexes can be searched. So it also considers how a change, or correction, to a Register Entry may be reflected in the GRO Index.</p>
